OL,3,CResidents of small Welsh town fear
OL,4,C'HGV driving through every two minutes'
OL,6,FMs Bolton added the road is already
OL,7,F"really dangerous" to walk along.
OL,9,FThat view was echoed by other
OL,10,Fprotestors, with one telling they are
OL,11,Falready too afraid to commute using a
OL,12,Fbike because of how busy the roads are.
OL,14,FAnother raised concerns about historic
OL,15,Fplanning permission for the quarry,
OL,16,Fwhich was granted before the area grew
OL,17,Fto what it is today.
